webpackJsonp([0x642923127f53],{1290:function(t,e){t.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{title:"Justin Ball",author:"Justin Ball"}},markdownRemark:{id:"/Users/jbasdf/projects/justinball/src/posts/2008-04-27-people-for-the-ethical-treatment-of-yeast-pety/index.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark",html:'<p>The next time you take a bite out of that yummy loaf of bread consider where it came from. Sure, cutting down all that nasty wheat is harmless enough. After all it\'s just a stupid plant. It doesn\'t have feelings. However, consider the condition of yeast.</p>\n<p>Here is how yeast is brought to market:</p>\n<p>How would you like to live in those conditions?</p>\n <img src="img_9274.jpg" />\n<p>After that kind of treatment being introduced into a warm, nutrient rich environment like this:\n<a href=""><img src="" alt="Bread Dough"></a>\nI am sure feels like heaven.</p>\n<p> []: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/jasmic/302657002/">http://www.flickr.com/photos/jasmic/302657002/</a></p>\n<p>but next comes this:\n<a href=""><img src="" alt="Bread Oven"></a>\nat 450 degrees. I can hear the shriek of millions of individual yeasts shrieking out in terror like Joan of Arc as they face their final moments in a fiery furness.</p>\n<p> []: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/bastian/2125007811/">http://www.flickr.com/photos/bastian/2125007811/</a></p>\n<p>So next time you eat this:\n<a href=""><img src="" alt="Bread"></a>\nJust think of the millions of dead bodies sacrificed so you can have light and fluffy bread.</p>\n<p> []: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/hlk/389341090/">http://www.flickr.com/photos/hlk/389341090/</a></p>\n<p>It\'s time to be PETY.</p>',frontmatter:{title:"People for the Ethical Treatment of Yeast (PETY)",date:"April 27, 2008",image:{childImageSharp:{sizes:{src:"/static/img_9274-c711ad88d84fb701550dcd6645a4eb8d-381d6.jpg"}}}}}},pathContext:{path:"/people-for-the-ethical-treatment-of-yeast-pety"}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---people-for-the-ethical-treatment-of-yeast-pety-272758ce530a706fad2a.js.map